race.comment: FLYING ARTIE (1) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in his head turning 19.32 win at this track over 342m. Has the ability and looks a key chance again. NANGAR LADY (3) recorded a win over the 530m at this track in a respectable 30.51 last start. Bold showing expected again. CANYA STRIKER (7) hit the ground running to win over the 730m at this track two runs back then prominent throughout when finishing second at this track last start. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Must be included in calculations. WHITE OWL (2) cannot be underestimated. Something for the Multiples: PRINCESS TILLEY (6)
